%20four%20decades%20plunged%20the%20country%20into%20the%20deepest%20turmoil%20in%20its%20modern%20democratic%20history%20and%20caught%20its%20close%20allies%20around%20the%20world%20off%20guard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%2C%20which%20stations%20nearly%2030%2C000%20troops%20in%20South%20Korea%20to%20protect%20it%20from%20the%20nuclear-armed%20North%2C%20initially%20voiced%20deep%20concern%20at%20the%20declaration%2C%20then%20relief%20that%20martial%20law%20was%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dramatic%20developments%20also%20left%20the%20future%20of%20Yoon%20--%20a%20conservative%20politician%20and%20former%20star%20public%20prosecutor%20who%20was%20elected%20president%20in%202022%20--%20in%20jeopardy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korea's%20main%20opposition%20party%20--%20whose%20lawmakers%20jumped%20fences%20and%20tussled%20with%20security%20forces%20so%20they%20could%20vote%20to%20overturn%20the%20law%20--%20demanded%20that%20Yoon%20step%20down%20immediately%20over%20the%20attempted%20%26quot%3Binsurrection%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nation's%20largest%20umbrella%20labour%20union%20also%20called%20an%20%26quot%3Bindefinite%20general%20strike%26quot%3B%20until%20Yoon%20resigned.%20And%20the%20leader%20of%20Yoon's%20own%20ruling%20party%20described%20the%20attempt%20as%20%26quot%3Btragic%26quot%3B%20while%20calling%20for%20those%20involved%20to%20be%20held%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoon%20backed%20down%20after%20lawmakers%20voted%20to%20oppose%20the%20declaration%2C%20which%20he%20made%20late%20on%20Tuesday%20night%20citing%20the%20threat%20of%20North%20Korea%20and%20%26quot%3Banti-state%20forces%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20a%20moment%20ago%2C%20there%20was%20a%20demand%20from%20the%20National%20Assembly%20to%20lift%20the%20state%20of%20emergency%2C%20and%20we%20have%20withdrawn%20the%20military%20that%20was%20deployed%20for%20martial%20law%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20Yoon%20said%20in%20a%20televised%20address%20around%204%3A30%20am%20(1930%20GMT%20Tuesday).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20accept%20the%20National%20Assembly's%20request%20and%20lift%20the%20martial%20law%20through%20the%20Cabinet%20meeting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYonhap%20news%20agency%20then%20reported%20that%20Yoon's%20cabinet%20had%20approved%20the%20motion%20to%20lift%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20aides%20working%20for%20Yoon%20offered%20Wednesday%20to%20resign%20en%20masse%20over%20the%20martial%20law%20declaration%2C%20Yonhap%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20start%20of%20the%20working%20day%2C%20Yoon%20had%20yet%20to%20reappear%20publicly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Impeachment'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20U-turn%20prompted%20jubilation%20among%20protesters%20outside%20parliament%20who%20had%20braved%20freezing%20temperatures%20to%20keep%20vigil%20through%20the%20night%20in%20defiance%20of%20Yoon's%20martial%20law%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemonstrators%20who%20had%20been%20waving%20South%20Korean%20flags%20and%20chanting%20%26quot%3BArrest%20Yoon%20Suk%20Yeol%26quot%3B%20outside%20the%20National%20Assembly%20erupted%20in%20cheers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELim%20Myeong-pan%2C%2055%2C%20told%20AFP%20that%20Yoon's%20decision%20to%20rescind%20martial%20law%20did%20not%20absolve%20him%20of%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYoon's%20act%20of%20imposing%20it%20in%20the%20first%20place%20without%20legitimate%20cause%20is%20a%20serious%20crime%20in%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20Lim%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20paved%20his%20own%20path%20to%20impeachment%20with%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefying%20security%20forces%2C%20190%20lawmakers%20managed%20to%20get%20into%20the%20assembly%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Wednesday%20and%20unanimously%20voted%20to%20oppose%20martial%20law.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20constitution%2C%20martial%20law%20must%20be%20lifted%20when%20a%20majority%20in%20par