%20law%20to%20be%20lifted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%2C%20hundreds%20of%20protesters%20gathered%2C%20many%20raising%20chants%20calling%20for%20Yoon%20to%20be%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20What%20happened%20next%3F%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20lawmakers'%20vote%2C%20Yoon%20backed%20down.%20His%20cabinet%20additionally%20approved%20the%20motion%20to%20lift%20the%20order%2C%20Yonhap%20news%20agency%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20a%20moment%20ago%2C%20there%20was%20a%20demand%20from%20the%20National%20Assembly%20to%20lift%20the%20state%20of%20emergency%2C%20and%20we%20have%20withdrawn%20the%20military%20that%20was%20deployed%20for%20martial%20law%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20Yoon%20said%20in%20a%20televised%20address%20around%204%3A30%20am%20(1930%20GMT%20Tuesday).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20South%20Korea's%20constitution%2C%20the%20parliamentary%20vote%20to%20lift%20martial%20law%20has%20to%20be%20respected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Why%20did%20Yoon%20do%20this%3F%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoon%20said%20he%20was%20acting%20to%20safeguard%20his%20country's%20liberal%20democracy%20from%20%26quot%3Banti-state%20elements%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bthreats%20posed%20by%20North%20Korea%26quot%3B%20--%20but%20gave%20little%20detail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20unexpected%2C%20the%20announcement%20came%20in%20the%20context%20of%20a%20festering%20budget%20row%20between%20Yoon%20and%20the%20opposition%20Democratic%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20slashed%20around%204.1%20trillion%20won%20(%242.8%20billion)%20from%20Yoon's%20proposed%20677%20trillion%20won%20budget%20for%20next%20year%2C%20prompting%20the%20president%20to%20complain%20that%20%26quot%3Ball%20key%20budgets%20essential%20to%20the%20nation's%20core%20functions%26quot%3B%20were%20being%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20clear%20is%20that%20Yoon%20has%20been%20a%20deeply%20unpopular%2C%20ineffec