0Anthropic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20strides%20could%20push%20AWS%20further%20into%20competition%20with%20other%20tech%20firms%20in%20the%20ongoing%20AI%20arms%20race%2C%20including%20AI%20chip%20giant%20Nvidia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20four%20takeaways%20from%20Garman's%20full%20keynote%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2282b805d5-a090-4c18-9734-ca0d389b33e8%5C%22%3EAWS'%20Trainium%20chips%20could%20compete%20with%20Nvidia.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20currently%20dominates%20the%20AI%20chip%20market%20with%20its%20sought-after%20and%20pricey%20GPUs%2C%20but%20Garman%20backed%20AWS's%20homegrown%20silicon%20during%20his%20keynote%20on%20Tuesday.%20His%20company's%20goal%20is%20to%20reduce%20the%20cost%20of%20AI%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20there's%20really%20only%20one%20choice%20on%20the%20GPU%20side%2C%20and%20it's%20just%20Nvidia.%20We%20think%20that%20customers%20would%20appreciate%20having%20multiple%20choices%2C%26quot%3B%20Garman%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Famazon-announces-supercomputer-new-server-powered-by-homegrown-ai-chips-18c196fc%3Fmod%3Dhp_lead_pos3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20growing%20rapidly%2C%20and%20the%20demand%20for%20chips%20that%20make%20the%20technology%20possible%20is%20poised%20to%20grow%20alongside%20it.%20Major%20tech%20companies%2C%20like%20Google%20and%20Microsoft%2C%20are%20venturing%20into%20chip%20creation%20as%20well%20to%20find%20an%20alternative%20to%20Nvidia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Garman%20told%20The%20Journal%20the%20doesn't%20expect%20Trainium%20to%20dethrone%20Nvidia%20%26quot%3Bfor%20a%20long%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%2C%20hopefully%2C%20Trainium%20can%20carve%20out%20a%20good%20niche%20where%20I%20actually%20think%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20great%20option%20for%20many%20workloads%20%E2%80%94%20not%20all%20workloads%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAWS%20also%20introduced%20Trainium3%2C%20its%20next-gen%20chip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b302cfa-9c7a-4bad-a271-6fb9735c4762%5C%22%3EAWS'%20new%20supercomputer%20could%20go%20toe%20to%20toe%20with%20Elon%20Musk's%20xAI.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20The%20Journal%2C%20the%20chip%20cluster%20known%20as%20Project%20Rainier%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20available%20in%202025.%20Once%20it%20is%20ready%2C%20Anthropic%20plans%20to%20use%20it%20to%20train%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20%26quot%3Bhundreds%20of%20thousands%26quot%3B%20of%20Trainium%20chips%2C%20it%20would%20challenge%20Elon%20Musk's%20xAI's%20Colossus%20%E2%80%94%20a%20supercomputer%20with%20100%2C000%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-hunger-for-chips-taxing-nvidia-supply-chain-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia's%20Hopper%20chips%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226fd5ee2a-7f46-4657-bef3-ff75779cb4a1%5C%22%3EApple%20is%20considering%20Trainium%202%20for%20Apple%20Intelligence%20training.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGarman%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-chip-design-silicon-secret-weapon-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20of%20its%20customers%20using%20AWS%20chips%2C%20like%20Amazon%20Graviton%20and%20Inferentia%2C%20for%20services%20including%20Siri.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBenoit%20Dupin%2C%20senior%20director%20of%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%20at%20Apple%2C%20then%20took%20to%20the%20stage%20at%20the%20Las%20Vegas%20conference.%20He%20said%20the%20company%20worked%20with%20AWS%20for%20%26quot%3Bvirtually%20all%20phases%26quot%3B%20of%20its%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%20life%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20unique%20elements%20of%20Apple%20business%20is%20the%20scale%20at%20which%20we%20operate%20and%20the%20speed%20with%20which%20we%20innovate%2C%26quot%3B%20Dupin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BAWS%20has%20been%20able%20to%20keep%20the%20pace%2C%20and%20we've%20been%20customers%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Dupin%20said%20Apple%20is%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20testing%20Trainium%202%20chips%20to%20potentially%20help%20train%20Apple%20Intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225dac81b4-55ea-427d-8a8d-ec65005ef268%5C%22%3EThe%20company%20introduced%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20foundational%20models%2C%20Amazon%20Nova.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmazon%20announced%20some%20new%20kids%20on%20the%20GenAI%20block.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAWS%20customers%20will%20be%20able%20to%20use%20Amazon%20Nova-powered%20GenAI%20applications%20%26quot%3Bto%20understand%20videos%2C%20charts%2C%20and%20documents%2C%20or%20generate%20videos%20and%20other%20multimedia%20content%2C%26quot%3B%20Amazon%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aboutamazon.com%2Fnews%2Faws%2Famazon-nova-artificial-intelligence-bedrock-aws%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20There%20are%20a%20range%20of%20models%20available%20at%20different%20costs%2C%20it%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BAmazon%20Nova%20Micro%2C%20Amazon%20Nova%20Lite%2C%20and%20Amazon%20Nova%20Pro%20are%20at%20least%2075%25%20less%20expensive%20than%20the%20best-performing%20models%20in%20their%20respective%20intelligence%20classes%20in%20Amazon%20Bedrock%2C%26quot%3B%20Amazon%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-new-planned-supercomputer-at-aws-conference-trainium-nova-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733270383000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674f7521ef9a5d904789c396%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.b