e-strikes-down-elon-musk-tesla-pay-package-second-time-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla's%20shareholder%20vote%20wasn't%20enough%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20pass%20Elon%20Musk's%20%2455%20billion%20compensation%20package.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20called%20the%20decision%20%26quot%3Bwrong%26quot%3B%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FTesla%2Fstatus%2F1863730393930735634%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20would%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20ruling%2C%20if%20not%20overturned%2C%20means%20that%20judges%20and%20plaintiffs'%20lawyers%20run%20Delaware%20companies%20rather%20than%20their%20rightful%20owners%20%E2%80%94%20the%20shareholders%2C%26quot%3B%20Tesla%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20happens%20next%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETesla%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20files%20an%20appeal%2C%20Delaware's%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20review%20the%20decision%20of%20Delaware%20Chancery%20Court%20Judge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudge-strikes-down-elon-musk-tesla-compensation-pay-package-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKathaleen%20St.%20J.%20McCormick%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20maintained%20her%20earlier%20ruling%20that%20struck%20down%20the%20pay%20package%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20Musk%20could%20have%20influenced%20Tesla's%20board%20members%2C%20to%20whom%20he%20had%20close%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMathieu%20Shapiro%2C%20Obermayer's%20managing%20partner%20and%20a%20member%20of%20its%20litigation%20department%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20appeals%20processes%20often%20take%20a%20year%20or%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShapiro%2C%20who%20focuses%20on%20business%20and%20commercial%20litigation%2C%20said%20the%20case%20will%20ultimately%20have%20to%20balance%20Delaware's%20freedom%20for%20companies%20to%20self-govern%20with%20concerns%20about%20excessive%20payouts%20and%20Musk's%20status%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20successful%20businessmen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20appeals%20are%20generally%20difficult%20to%20win%2C%20Shapiro%20said%20Musk's%20case%20is%20%26quot%3Bnovel%26quot%3B%20and%20contains%20unpredictable%20elements.%20One%20issue%20that%20may%20come%20up%20is%20whether%20Musk%20influenced%20the%20negotiations%20over%20his%20Tesla%20pay%20package%2C%20as%20the%20trial%20judge%20suggested%20in%20her%20initial%20ruling%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLittle%20law%20addresses%20executive%20compensation%2C%20let%20alone%20what%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20largest-ever%20compensation%20deal%20at%20a%20US%20public%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Shapiro%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20Musk's%20pay%20package%20was%20set%20to%20be%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musks-pay-package-compared-highest-paid-ceos-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elargest%20ever%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20CEO%2C%20there%20aren't%20many%20cases%20to%20turn%20to%20for%20direct%20precedent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnat%20Alon-Beck%2C%20a%20business%20law%20professor%20at%20Case%20Western%20Reserve%20University%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20one%20case%20that%20stands%20out%20is%20the%202015%20Delaware%20Chancery%20Court%20decision%20ruling%20against%20Mark%20Zuckerberg's%20attempt%20to%20ratify%20board%20actions%20related%20to%20Facebook's%202010%20acquisition%20of%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlon-Beck%2C%20who%20used%20to%20work%20as%20a%20merger%20and%20acquisition%20attorney%20for%20tech%20companies%20and%20also%20specializes%20in%20Delaware%20deal%20law%2C%20said%20Zuckerberg%20didn't%20follow%20the%20proper%20procedural%20requirements%20mandated%20by%20state%20law.%20The%20case%20demonstrates%20that%20even%20controlling%20shareholders%20need%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20legal%20procedures%20for%20ratifying%20board%20decisions%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20know%20Delaware%20law%2C%20you%20know%20that%20stuff%20like%20that%20is%20just%20not%20going%20to%20fly%2C%26quot%3B%20Alon-Beck%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColumbia%20law%20professor%20Dorothy%20Lund%20used%20to%20clerk%20for%20a%20Delaware%20Supreme%20Court%20justice%20and%20US%20Court%20of%20Appeals%20judge.%20She%20told%20BI%20that%20Delaware%20is%20also%20%26quot%3Bin%20a%20weird%20spot%26quot%3B%20because%20Tesla%20reincorporated%20from%20Delaware%20to%20Texas%20in%20June%2C%20and%20Musk%20has%20repeatedly%20spoken%20out%20about%20Delaware%20courts%20(he%20called%20the%20ruling%20%26quot%3Babsolute%20corruption%26quot%3B%20on%20Monday).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20decisions%20aren't%20supposed%20to%20be%20influenced%20by%20concerns%20around%20public%20perception%2C%20Lund%20said%20Musk's%20behavior%20hasn't%20been%20the%20most%20strategic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelaware%20now%20has%20to%20worry%20about%20looking%20like%2C%20well%2C%20if%20we%20reverse%2C%20do%20we%20just%20look%20like%20we%20got%20cowed%20by%20Elon%20Musk%3F%26quot%3B%20Lund%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22db518daa-ec96-4a3c-9761-798b2ae7161d%5C%22%3EReintroducing%20the%20pay%20package%20in%20Texas%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20the%20shareholder%20vote%2C%20Tesla%20board%20chair%20Robyn%20Denholm%20said%20in%20June%20that%20the%20board%20had%20considered%20introducing%20a%20new%20pay%20plan%20if%20the%20shareholder%20vote%20didn't%20pass%20%E2%80%94%20an%20option%20she%20said%20would%20cost%20shareholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Tesla%20created%20a%20new%20plan%20with%20the%20same%20stock%20grants%2C%20it%20would%20cost%20tens%20of%20billions%20in%20stock-based%20compensation%20today.%20That's%20because%20the%20compensation%20tied%20to%20the%20original%20package%20was%20worth%20an%20estimated%20%242.3%20billion%20in%20stock%2C%20and%20it's%20already%20been%20paid%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlon-Beck%20told%20BI%20that%20a%20new%20compensation%20package%20in%20Texas%20would%20make%20the%20most%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20do%20a%20new%20vote%20in%20Texas%2C%20under%20Texas%20law%2C%20and%20I%20would%20authorize%20a%20new%20compensation%20package%2C%26quot%3B%20Alon-Beck%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20old%20package%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20be%20authorized%20because%20of%20a%20conflict%20of%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShapiro%20said%20he%20thinks%20it%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bvery%20difficult%26quot%3B%20to%20draft%20the%20same%20package%20in%20Texas%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20original%20plan%20goes%20back%20to%202018%20and%20was%20based%20on%20specific%20targets%20as%20well%20as%20Tesla's%20stock%20price%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShapiro%20said%20Musk's%20decision%20to%20appeal%20or%20reintroduce%20the%20package%20in%20Texas%20depends%20on%20multiple%20factors%20%E2%80%94%20and%20underlying%20motivations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20may%20be%20all%20about%20the%20money%2C%20the%20case%20may%20also%20signify%20more%20about%20public%20companies%20in%20the%20US%20and%20the%20way%20in%20which%20shareholders%20and%20courts%20can%20interfere%20with%20management's%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOr%20is%20it%20about%20his%20public%20persona%20and%20his%20reputation%20and%20how%20those%20things%20are%20understood%20in%20future%20business%20dealings%2C%26quot%3B%20Shapiro%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20he%20were%20my%20client%2C%20I%20would%20have%20a%20discussion%20about%20all%20of%20those%20things%20before%20deciding%20what%20path%20forward%20was%20best%20for%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-pay-package-next-steps-appeal-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733263779000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674f2f4f9e9761932b4a55bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2