to%20the%20Bay%20Area%2C%20renting%20made%20sense%20from%20a%20budget%20perspective%3A%20It%20was%20cheaper%20for%20them%20to%20rent%20in%20the%20pricey%20city%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20still%20is%2C%20said%20Nader%3A%20%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20San%20Francisco%20really%20favors%20renting.%20It's%20really%20hard%20from%20a%20pure%20numbers%20standpoint%20to%20make%20owning%20make%20sense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22andre%20nader%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674f62559e9761932b4a68e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224128%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Nader%20family%20resides%20in%20San%20Francisco.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Mini%20Anna%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20exceptions%2C%20he%20noted%3A%20%26quot%3BParticularly%20in%20a%20place%20like%20San%20Francisco%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20math%20can%20change%20with%20the%20appreciation%20of%20property%20values.%20If%20housing%20prices%20continue%20to%20increase%2C%20then%20maybe%20buying%20can%20come%20out%2C%20but%20if%20you%20take%20conservative%20approaches%20to%20any%20future%20increases%20in%20housing%2C%20renting%20just%20ends%20up%20making%20a%20lot%20more%20sense%20mathematically.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20Nader%20was%20never%20convinced%20he%20and%20his%20family%20would%20stay%20in%20San%20Francisco%20long%20enough%20to%20make%20buying%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Goldilocks%20timeline%20has%20historically%20been%2C%20five%20to%20seven%20years%20is%20when%20buying%20starts%20being%20more%20advantageous%20than%20renting%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%20when%20I%20do%20the%20numbers%2C%20it's%20even%20longer%20%E2%80%94%20closer%20to%20the%2010-year%20timeframe%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I'd%20never%20been%20confident%20that%20I%20would%20be%20in%20San%20Francisco%20that%20long.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20prudent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investors-financial-independence-how-to-buy-invest-property-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereal%20estate%20investing%20is%20a%20viable%20path%20to%20wealth%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Nader%20doesn't%20believe%20he%20needs%20to%20own%20property%20to%20hit%20his%20financial%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-millionaire-breaks-down-his-simple-investment-strategy-index-funds-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestment%20strategy%20revolves%20around%20low-cost%20index%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20owns%20various%20Fidelity%20and%20Vanguard%20index%20funds%2C%20including%20Vanguard%20Total%20Stock%20Market%20Index%20Fund%20ETF%20Shares%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fvanguard-total-stock-market-index-fund-etf-shares-us9229087690%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVTI%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20Vanguard%20Total%20International%20Stock%20Index%20Fund%20ETF%20Shares%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fvanguard-total-international-stock-index-fund-etf-shares-us9219097683%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVXUS%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENader%20describes%20the%20strategy%20as%20%26quot%3Bsuper%20boring%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it's%20effective%3A%20It's%20helped%20him%20build%20a%20seven-figure%20net%20worth%2C%20which%20BI%20verified%20by%20looking%20at%20a%20copy%20of%20his%20investment%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20lost%20on%20him%20that%20bringing%20in%20two%20tech%20incomes%20was%20a%20major%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20won%20the%20income%20game%20by%20being%20in%20tech%2C%20by%20being%20a%20dual-income%20household.%20I%20didn't%20need%20to%20be%20taking%20these%20outsized%20risks%20by%20investing%20in%20extremely%20speculative%20ways.%20I%20could%20be%20boring%20in%20my%20portfolio%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nader%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20Meta%20for%20nine%20years%20before%20he%20was%20affected%20by%20the%20company's%202023%20layoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20his%20wife%20had%20enough%20between%20their%20savings%20and%20one%20tech%20income%20that%20he%20didn't%20have%20to%20find%20another%20job%2C%20but%20he%20says%20he'll%20consider%20himself%20%26quot%3Bsemi-FIRE'd%26quot%3B%20until%20his%20wife%20also%20walks%20away%20from%20her%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENader%2C%20who%20spends%20his%20days%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fandrenader.substack.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewriting%20on%20Substack%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20doing%20one-on-one%20financial%20independence%20coaching%2C%20says%20his%20investment%20strategy%20has%20remained%20the%20same%20since%20the%20layoff.%20He%20likes%20the%20hands-off%20approach%20to%20index%20fund%20investing%2C%20especially%20after%20experiencing%20what%20it's%20like%20to%20own%20real%20estate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20was%20managing%20the%20Austin%20rental%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20kind%20of%20quickly%20realized%20that%20the%20promise%20of%20real%20estate%20being%20a%20clearly%20passive%20investment%2C%20even%20if%20you%20have%20property%20managers%2C%20wasn't%20something%20that%2C%20for%20me%2C%20proved%20to%20be%20true%2C%20so%20it%20further%20reinforced%20my%20view%20around%20focusing%20on%20super%20boring%2C%20low-fee%20index%20funds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20could%20have%20a%20few%20hundred%20thousand%20dollars%20in%20real%20estate%20and%20maybe%20a%20million%20dollars%20in%20index%20funds%2C%20but%20I%20would%20be%20thinking%20about%20the%20real%20estate%20three%20times%20as%20much%2C%20so%20it%20would%20be%20a%20disproportionate%20amount%20of%20mental%20exercise%2C%20at%20least%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuying-home-renting-san-francisco-real-estate-fire-retirement-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2F