investors%20have%20seemed%20to%20think%20there's%20some%20kind%20of%20good%20news%20coming%3A%20They%20have%20pushed%20up%20BuzzFeed%20shares%20more%20than%2072%25%20in%20that%20time%20(though%20shares%20have%20dropped%20by%20as%20much%20as%205%25%20today).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20when%20BuzzFeed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fir.buzzfeed.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fnews-release-details%2Fbuzzfeed-inc-delivers-strong-q3-financial-results%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20quarterly%20earnings%2C%20it%20promised%20investors%20that%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20coming%20weeks%2C%20we%20look%20forward%20to%20sharing%20an%20update%20on%20our%20debt%2C%20balance%20sheet%2C%20Q4%20financial%20outlook%2C%20and%20the%20results%20of%20the%20strategic%20review%20process%20we%20initiated%20last%20year%20with%20our%20financial%20advisors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20educated%20hunch%20is%20that%20the%20update-to-be%20will%20happen%20later%20this%20week.%20But%20right%20now%2C%20BuzzFeed%20PR%20isn't%20commenting.%20I've%20also%20asked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvivek-ramaswamy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVivek%20Ramaswamy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20investor%20and%20soon-to-be%20DOGE%20cochair%20advising%20the%20next%20Trump%20administration%2C%20for%20comment.%20That's%20because%20earlier%20this%20year%20Ramaswamy%20amassed%20a%209%25%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F1828972%2F000200799724000014%2FxslSCHEDULE_13D_X01%2Fprimary_doc.xml%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estake%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20BuzzFeed%20and%20issued%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuzzfeed-vivek-ramawsamy-letter-jonah-peretti-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eset%20of%20demands%20to%20CEO%20Jonah%20Peretti%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20Peretti%20seems%20to%20have%20ignored.%20Ramaswamy%20has%20not%20responded%20to%20my%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20t