chief%20adviser%20Mohamed%20Yunus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20West%20also%20mentioned%20concerns%20raised%20by%20New%20Delhi%20over%20the%20happenings%20in%20Bangladesh.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20statement%20of%20concern%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%20following%20the%20arrest%20of%20Chinmoy%20Krishna%20Das%2C%20a%20well-known%20Hindu%20leader%2C%20on%20sedition%20charges.%20The%20UK%20Foreign%2C%20Commonwealth%20and%20Development%20Office%20(FCDO)%20desk%20is%20closely%20monitoring%20those%20developments%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20%26quot%3BThe%20UK%20government%20will%20continue%20to%20monitor%20the%20situation%2C%20including%20making%20representations%20from%20this%20House%2C%20and%20will%20engage%20with%20the%20interim%20government%20in%20Bangladesh%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20freedom%20of%20religion%20or%20belief%20specifically%20as%20it%20affects%20the%20Hindu%20community.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConservative%20MP%20Priti%20Patel%2C%20who%20is%20the%20Shadow%20Secretary%20of%20State%20for%20Foreign%20Affairs%20called%20the%20situation%20in%20Bangladesh%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%2C%20deeply%20concerning%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20surge%20in%20incidents%20of%20violence%2C%20vandalism%2C%20and%20desecration%20targeting%20Hindu%20minorities%2C%20Ms%20Patel%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20degree%20of%20escalation%20in%20violence%20is%20deeply%20concerning.%20What%20we%20are%20witnessing%20now%20is%20uncontrolled%20violence%20in%20many%20quarters.%20We%20are%20watching%20with%20horror%20and%20shock%20as%20further%20violence%20spreads%20in%20Bangladesh.%20The%20thoughts%20of%20all%20of%20us%20in%20the%20House%20are%20with%20the%20diaspora%20community%20here%20and%20those%20affected%20in%20Bangladesh.%20These%20are%20deeply%20disturbing%20reports.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5