2engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdonald-trump-jr-says-as-a-father-he-understands-bidens-pardon-but-%2Farticleshow%2F115946276.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdonald-trump-jr-says-as-a-father-he-understands-bidens-pardon-but-%2Famp_articleshow%2F115946276.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdonald-trump-jr-says-as-a-father-he-understands-bidens-pardon-but-%2Famp_articleshow%2F115946276.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chandni%20Chowk%20Was%20Among%20Least%20Polluted%20In%20Delhi%20For%202%20Days.%20Here's%20Why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChandni%20Chowk%20was%20among%20the%20least%20polluted%20spots%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Monday%20and%20Tuesday%2C%20data%20provided%20by%20pollution%20monitoring%20bodies%20showed%2C%20as%20the%20overall%20air%20quality%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20improved%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bpoor%26quot%3B%20category%20-%20after%20a%20month-long%20spell%20of%20%26quot%3Bvery%20poor%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsevere%26quot%3B%20categories%20-%20three%20days%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Delhi's%20oldest%20and%20busiest%20markets%2C%20and%20a%20tourist%20hub%2C%20Chandni%20Chowk%20recorded%20an%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%20of%20186%20(moderate)%20at%208am%20on%20Monday%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Tropical%20Meteorology%20(IITM)%20that%20set%20up%20a%20monitoring%20station%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20AQI%20oscillated%20in%20the%20250-270%20bracket%20during%20the%20day%2C%20under%20the%20%26quot%3Bpoor%26quot%3B%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20areas%20in%20the%20city%2C%20however%2C%20mostly%20recorded%20an%20air%20quality%20that%20remained%20under%20the%20%26quot%3Bvery%20poor%26quot%3B%20category.%20At%204pm%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Shadipur%20recorded%20an%20AQI%20of%20324%2C%20Anand%20Vihar%20311%20and%20Mundka%20310%2C%20according%20to%20data%20provided%20by%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board.%20Data%20for%20other%20areas%20for%20Monday%20was%20not%20immediately%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20national%20capital%20recorded%20an%20AQI%20of%20285%20on%20Sunday%2C%20280%20on%20Monday%20and%20268%20on%20Tuesday%20-%20all%20of%20which%20fall%20under%20the%20%26quot%3Bpoor%26quot%3B%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20and%20experts%20said%20the%20primary%20reason%20behind%20the%20relatively%20low%20AQI%20in%20Chandni%20Chowk%20was%20the%20absence%20of%20motor%20vehicles%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20Delhi%20transport%20department%20had%20notified%20the%20area%2C%20which%20was%20then%20under%20development%2C%20as%20a%20non-motorised%20zone.%20According%20to%20the%20notification%2C%20no%20motor%20vehicle%20shall%20be%20allowed%20to%20ply%20on%20the%20main%20Chandni%20Chowk%20Road%20from%20Red%20Fort%20to%20Fatehpuri%20Mosque%20from%209%20am%20to%209%20pm%20on%20all%20days.%20Currently%2C%20only%20cycle%20rickshaws%20are%20permitted%20in%20the%20area.%20However%2C%20the%20restrictions%20shall%20not%20be%20applicable%20in%20the%20case%20of%20emergencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20restriction%20on%20vehicles%20in%20Chandni%20Chowk%20does%20help%20solve%20the%20pollution%20problem.%20Only%20vehicles%20carrying%20essential%20goods%20are%20permitted.%20The%20ban%20on%20BS3%20and%20BS4%20vehicles%20(having%20high%20emissions)%20has%20also%20helped%20keep%20a%20check%20on%20the%20pollution.%20But%20this%20is%20a%20collective%20effort.%20Just%20curbing%20vehicular%20movement%20will%20not%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20Additional%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(Traffic%20Headquarters)%20Satya%20Vir%20Katara%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Sachin%20Ghude%2C%20a%20scientist%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Tropical%20Meteorology%2C%20which%20set%20up%20the%20air%20quality%20monitoring%20station%20in%20Chandni%20Chowk%2C%20also%20attributed%20the%20improved%20air%20quality%20to%20the%20traffic%20curbs%20in%20the%20area.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20this%20is%20the%20best%20example%20of%20how%20you%20manage%20the%20traffic%2C%20and%20if%20you%20create%20a%20non-motorised%20zone%2C%20you%20will%20have%20an%20improvement%20in%20the%20AQI%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20study%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20Science%20and%20Environment%20last%20month%20said%2051.5%25%20of%20the%20pollution%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20is%20caused%20by%20transport%20and%20vehicular%20emission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20MP%20George%2C%20a%20former%20scientist%20at%20Delhi%20Pollution%20Control%20Committee%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3B...Only%20if%20there%20is%20a%20consistent%20downward%20trend%2C%20can%20it%20be%20considered%20a%20legitimate%20improvement%20in%20the%20air%20quality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733251320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-10%2Fqi7cr79o_chandni-chowk-motorfree-corridor-650_625x300_29_October_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandni-chowk-was-among-least-polluted-in-delhi-for-2-days-heres-why-7165744%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chandni%20Chowk%20was%20among%20the%20least%20polluted%20spots%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Monday%20and%20Tuesday%2C%20data%20provided%20by%20pollution%20monitoring%20bodies%20showed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandni-chowk-was-among-least-polluted-in-delhi-for-2-days-heres-why-7165744%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Violence%20in%20B%E2%80%99desh%20%E2%80%98attempt%20at%20ethnic%20cleansing%20of%20Hindus%E2%80%99%3A%20UK%20MP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733251076000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-11594604