rict%20public%20vehicles%20under%20tight%20security%20from%20Imphal%20to%20hill%20districts%20from%20Wednesday%20amid%20a%20lull%20in%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20the%20state%2C%20according%20to%20an%20official%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20be%20the%20administration's%20second%20attempt%20to%20resume%20public%20transport%20service%20in%2019%20months%20in%20the%20state%20which%20has%20been%20witnessing%20clashes%20between%20the%20valley-dominant%20Meitei%20community%20and%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20dominant%20in%20Churachandpur%20and%20some%20other%20hill%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20state%20government%20has%20reviewed%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20state%20with%20the%20availability%20of%20security%20forces%2C%20response%20system%20and%20feasibility%20inputs%20from%20different%20agencies%20and%20has%20decided%20to%20resume%20traffic%20of%20public%20vehicles%20with%20adequate%20security%20deployment%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Secretary%20Vineet%20Joshi%20said%20in%20an%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublic%20vehicles%20will%20be%20operated%20from%20Imphal%20to%20Senapati%20via%20Kangpokpi%2C%20and%20from%20Imphal%20to%20Churachandpur%20via%20Bishnupur%20from%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Senapati%20is%20a%20Naga-dominated%20area%2C%20Kangpokpi%20and%20Churachandpur%20are%20Kuki-dominated%20areas.%20Imphal%20and%20Bishnupur%20are%20Meitei-dominated%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bmovement%20will%20be%20restricted%20to%20fixed%20hours%20only%20and%20general%20public%20desirous%20of%20joining%20the%20route%20are%20informed%20to%20contact%20respective%20offices%20of%20the%20Deputy%20Commissioners%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20initiative%20taken%20up%20by%20the%20state%20government%20is%20aimed%20at%20alleviating%20grievances%20faced%20by%20the%20general%20public%20in%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20appealed%20to%20t