ted%20will%20be%20discussed%20in%20the%20next%20meeting%20on%20January%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20very%20straightforward%20with%20MHA%20officials%20and%20took%20up%20issues%20concerning%20youth%20and%20employment%2C%20and%20we%20have%20been%20assured%20that%20our%20concerns%20are%20genuine%20and%20will%20be%20addressed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20details%20whether%20we%20would%20get%20a%20separate%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20or%20will%20it%20be%20merged%20with%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20are%20going%20to%20be%20worked%20out%20in%20the%20next%20meeting.%20But%20this%20meeting%20was%20good%20and%20our%20voices%20were%20heard%20by%20ministry%20officials%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20BJP%20MP%20Thupstan%20Chhewang%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20meeting%20began%2C%20a%20list%20of%20doables%20were%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20over%20400%20posts%20vacant%2C%20and%20we%20have%20been%20assured%20they%20would%20go%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20and%20tribals%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chhewang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20months%20of%20the%20stalled%20dialogue%2C%20the%20Leh%20Apex%20Body%20(LAB)%20and%20the%20Kargil%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(KDA)%2C%20an%20amalgam%20of%20social%2C%20political%2C%20trade%2C%20students%20and%20religious%20groups%20from%20Ladakh%2C%20met%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20Nityanand%20Rai%2C%20Union%20Home%20Secretary%20Govind%20Mohan%2C%20and%20MHA%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delegation%20has%20been%20seeking%20statehood%20for%20Ladakh%20to%20ensure%20people's%20participation%20in%20governance%2C%20administrative%20efficiency%2C%20better%20governance%2C%20and%20economic%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20second%20demand%20includes%20pushing%20for%20Ladakh's%20inclusion%20under%20the%206th%20Schedule%20for%20grea