as%20a%20new%20acquaintance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWas%2040%20minutes%20enough%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F266934%2Ftwitter-viral-thread-shibu-padmini-vaidyanathan-social-media-friendships%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20friendship%20to%20be%20forged%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%20not%2C%20as%20Gopika%20discovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20most%20of%20these%20play%20dates%2C%20she%20would%20end%20up%20playing%20with%20the%20child%2C%20while%20Vir%20wandered%20off.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20stressful%20for%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20used%20to%20be%20very%20reticent%20and%20it%20was%20hard%20for%20him%20to%20open%20up%20to%20a%20new%20child%20every%20time.%E2%80%9D%20So%2C%20today%2C%20when%20she%20watches%20her%20son%20bond%20with%20Mihaan%20without%20any%20intervention%2C%20relief%20colours%20her%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241031-WA0097-1733201406-500x519.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vir%20with%20his%20mom%20Gopika%20who%20is%20one%20part%20of%20the%20duo%20that%20has%20created%20Buddy%20Up%2C%20a%20friendship%20app%20for%20those%20with%20disabilities%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241031-WA0097-1733201406-500x519.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241031-WA0097-1733201406-289x300.jpg%20289w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241031-WA0097-1733201406-150x156.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241031-W