%20in%20awe%20and%20makes%20it%20a%20point%20to%20express%20it%20every%20chance%20he%20gets.%20Vir%20appreciates%20this.%20Sharing%20his%20uncomfortable%20history%20of%20making%20new%20friends%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20easier%20when%20someone%20comes%20up%20to%20me%20and%20says%20they%20want%20to%20be%20my%20friend%20instead%20of%20the%20other%20way%20around.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FBuddy-Up-friendship-app-for-disabled-people-1-1733201748.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Moneisha%20with%20her%20son%20Mihaan%20who%20is%20also%20a%20Down%20Syndrome%20advocate%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FBuddy-Up-friendship-app-for-disabled-people-1-1733201748.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FBuddy-Up-friendship-app-for-disabled-people-1-1733201748-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FBuddy-Up-friendship-app-for-disabled-people-1-1733201748-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FBuddy-Up-friendship-app-for-disabled-people-1-1733201748-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FBuddy-Up-friendship-app-for-disabled-people-1-1733201748-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-385502%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMoneisha%20and%20her%20son%2C%20Mihaan%2C%20are%20advocates%20for%20Down%20syndrome%20awareness.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMihaan%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20a%20more%20perkier%20outlook%20on%20socialising.%20One%20of%20his%20closest%20friends%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%