F2024%2F11%2Ffile-9_11zon-1732801948-500x527.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-9_11zon-1732801948-285x300.jpg%20285w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-9_11zon-1732801948-150x158.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffile-9_11zon-1732801948.jpg%20620w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-384014%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22527%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJyoti%20Padma%E2%80%99s%20journey%20into%20dairy%20farming%20started%20because%20of%20her%20daughter.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetermined%20to%20provide%20her%20daughter%20with%20essential%20nutrients%2C%20Jyoti%20explored%20various%20milk%20brands%20and%20locally%20sourced%20options.%20However%2C%20her%20child%E2%80%99s%20body%20rejected%20every%20attempt.%20A%20breakthrough%20came%20in%202018%20when%20her%20sister%20from%20Lucknow%20sent%20milk%20from%20her%20farm.%20To%20Jyoti%E2%80%99s%20surprise%2C%20her%20daughter%20digested%20it%20without%20any%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fbetapadhaodeshjagao%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22BetaPadhaoDeshJagao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20was%20a%20pivotal%20revelation%20for%20Jyoti.%20She%20had%20been%20searching%20for%20the%20cause%20of%20her%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20struggles%2C%20only%20to%20realise%20that%20the%20problem%20had%20been%20the%20milk%20all%20along!%20%E2%80%9CPackaged%20and%20processed%20milk%20is%20a%20ba