y%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJyoti%E2%80%99s%20journey%20from%20a%20concerned%20mother%20to%20a%20successful%20entrepreneur%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20her%20unwavering%20dedication%20to%20quality%20and%20sustainability.%20Her%20ventures%20not%20only%20meet%20the%20growing%20demand%20for%20pure%20dairy%20products%20but%20also%20champion%20ethical%20farming%20practices.%20As%20she%20proudly%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20strive%20to%20ensure%20our%20cows%20are%20happy%20and%20healthy%2C%20and%20our%20customers%20feel%20connected%20to%20the%20source%20of%20their%20food.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CReal%20wealth%20is%20owning%20a%20cow%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parikshit%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Jyoti%20and%20Parikshit%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jerseygirlorganics.co.nz%2Fpost%2Fcan-you-drink-a2-milk-if-you-are-lactose-intolerant%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECan%20you%20drink%20A2%20milk%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20lactose%20intolerant%3F%E2%80%99%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Jersey%20Girl%20Organics%2C%20Published%20on%208%20November%2C%202021%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthline.com%2Fnutrition%2Fa1-vs-a2-milk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA1%20vs.%20A2%20Milk%20%E2%80%94%20Does%20It%20Matter%3F%E2%80%99%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Healthline%2C%20Published%20on%2017%20July%2C%202023%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbadgut.org%2Finformation-centre%2Fhealth-nut