most%20of%20whom%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F81965%2Fforeigners-indian-classical-music%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproducing%20Indian%20sounds%20in%20a%20completely%20different%20context%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20had%20a%20two-week%20production%20session%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20another%20month%20in%20Spain.%20Besides%20Michael%2C%20we%20also%20had%20another%20co-producer%20on%20board%20%E2%80%94%20my%20friend%20and%20accomplished%20percussionist%20Pramat%20Kiran%20from%20Bengaluru%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F8uBJzibp-XI%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26rel%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D1%26controls%3D1%26color%3Dred%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20about%20six%20years%20to%20complete%20this%20project%2C%20during%20which%20she%20also%20discovered%20her%20ability%20to%20engage%20in%20songwriting%2C%20specifically%20lyric%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMoreover%2C%20I%20had%20the%20honour%20of%20working%20with%20some%20of%20the%20most%20incredible%20musicians%20who%20are%20like%20heroes%20to%20me%2C%20alongside%20some%20of%20the%20best%20musicians%20from%20Bengaluru.%20The%20music%20on%20this%20album%20comes%20from%20their%20hearts%20and%20exemplifies%20their%20generosity%20of%20spirit%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20this%20generosity%20of%20spirit%20that%20also%20defines%20Varijashree%20as%20an%20artist%2C%20bridging%20the%20gap%20between%20different%20cultures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fvarijashree%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVarijashree%20Venugopal%2FInstagram%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732591800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_462140547_1749964079138896_5423463430645741798_n_1080-1732544639.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D382543%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Varijashree%20Venugopal%2C%20the%20extraordinary%20singer%2C%20flautist%2C%20and%20composer%20from%20Bengaluru%2C%20has%20been%20nominated%20for%20a%20prestigious%20Grammy%20Award%20this%20year%20for%20her%20contributions%20to%20the%20song%20'A%20Rock%20Somewhere'%2C%20a%20collaboration%20with%20multi-Grammy%20winner%20Jacob%20Collier%20and%20Anoushka%20Shankar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F382543%2Fvarijashree-venugopal-grammy-award-nomination-a-rock-somehwere-jacob-collier-anoushka-shankar-bengaluru%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Tribal%20Community%20In%20Maharashtra%20Is%20Using%20Zero-Budget%20Videos%20to%20Fight%20for%20Their%20Rights%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20quiet%20village%20of%20Dhadgaon%20in%20Nandurbar%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20a%20transformative%20movement%20is%20taking%20root.%20%E2%80%98Aadiwasi%20Janjagruti%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20grassroots%20initiative%20led%20by%2050%20passionate%20community%20members%20%E2%80%94%20is%20revolutionising%20how%20tribal%20communities%20connect%20with%20governance%20and%20the%20world.%20Through%20captivating%20videos%2C%20films%2C%20and%20documentaries%2C%20they%20are%20creating%20a%20hyperlocal%20communication%20network%20that%20empowers%20tribes%20to%20address%20everyday%20challenges%20and%20engage%20with%20the%20Government%20like%20never%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20it%20all%20began%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20Aadiwasi%20Janjagruti%20traces%20back%20to%202016%2C%20when%20Nitesh%20Bhardwaj%20(33)%2C%20one%20of%20its%20founders%2C%20arrived%20in%20Dhadgaon%20for%20a%20fellowship%20programme.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Nitesh%20was%20passionate%20about%20filmmaking%20but%20had%20no%20plans%20for%20long-term%20involvement%20in%20the%20village.%20His%20connection%20with%20the%20community%20began%20unexpectedly%20%E2%80%94%20through%20a%20group%20of%20eager%20high%20school%20students%20curious%20about%20video%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20equipment%20or%20resources%2C%20Nitesh%20started%20teaching%20the%20students%20how%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333099%2Fwomentaries-women-changemaker-stories-film-documentaries-winners-awards%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshoot%20and%20edit%20videos%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20just%20his%20and%20a%20friend%E2%80%99s%20phones.%20Their%20first%20project%20was%20a%20simple%2C%20zero-budget%20video%2C%20but%20its%20impact%20was%20profound.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fbetapadhaodeshjagao%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22BetaPadhaoDeshJagao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20uploaded%20it%20on%20YouTube%20and%20g